<% content_for :title, "Workspace | lending_rails" %>

<section class="flex flex-1 flex-col gap-8">
  <header class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 xl:flex-row xl:items-start xl:justify-between">
      <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-4">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-slate-500">Authenticated workspace</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">Lending operations workspace</h1>
          <p class="text-base leading-7 text-slate-600">
            Signed in as <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900"><%= Current.user.email_address %></span>. This protected entry point is the
            current starting place for the seeded-admin lending environment and reflects the live server-rendered application state.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap xl:max-w-md xl:justify-end">
        <%= link_to "Background jobs", "/jobs", class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:border-slate-400 hover:text-slate-950" %>
        <%= link_to "Health check", rails_health_check_path, class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:border-slate-400 hover:text-slate-950" %>
        <%= button_to "Sign out", session_path, method: :delete, class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-slate-950 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-slate-800" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section aria-label="Workspace overview" class="grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Current access</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-950">Admin-only protected entry</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
        Authentication, admin gating, and session persistence are active. Protected routes continue to redirect through the standard sign-in flow.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Available surfaces</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-950">Operational shell and job console</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
        Today&apos;s workspace is intentionally focused: a clear authenticated landing, access to background job operations, and platform health visibility.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Rendered now</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-950">Live server state</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
        Loaded on <span class="font-medium text-slate-800"><%= Time.current.strftime("%B %-d, %Y") %></span> from the current Rails application state,
        without placeholder borrower, loan, or dashboard metrics.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,2fr)_minmax(0,1fr)]">
    <article class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-950">What this workspace is for today</h2>
      <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
        <li>Confirm you are operating inside the protected lending administration environment.</li>
        <li>Start from a stable authenticated entry point before later stories add borrower, application, and loan workflows.</li>
        <li>End the session explicitly with the standard Rails sign-out flow when work is complete.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <aside class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-950 p-8 text-slate-100 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Session safety</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300">
        Signing out removes the persisted session and returns you to the login flow, so protected screens require authentication again.
      </p>
    </aside>
  </section>
</section>
